org.hari10.com.beans.base

Class BaseBean<T extends IEntity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hari10.com.beans.base.BaseBean<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - BaseBean entity type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccountBean, CityBean, CustomerBean, OperationBean

    public abstract class BaseBean<T extends IEntity>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Base bean class. Other jsf backing beans extends this class to get basic crud functionality + out of box search functionality. Bean should be ViewScoped.
    Author:
    Ignas
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
